text: Anastassiya Bannova is an archer from Kazakhstan. She was born on 26 February 1989. Bannova competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Anastasiya BannovaAnastassiya BANNOVA == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani archers Category:Olympians for Kazakhstan
